# SSH Server Configuration

# Network
Port 22
AddressFamily inet
ListenAddress 0.0.0.0

# Authentication
PubkeyAuthentication yes
PasswordAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM yes

# Root login
PermitRootLogin no

# Security
X11Forwarding no
MaxAuthTries 3
MaxSessions 5
LoginGraceTime 30

# Keep alive
ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2

# Logging
SyslogFacility AUTH
LogLevel INFO
